"title": "9412: heaven, worship and service in",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "9412: heaven, worship and service in",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>All in heaven engage continuously in the worship of God, while they perfectly carry out his will.</p>\n<h2>All heaven worships God</h2>\n<h3>The multitude in heaven and the twenty-four elders</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:6-Rev19:7\">REV 19:6–19:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:6\">NEH 9:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev4:6-Rev4:11\">REV 4:6–4:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:11-Rev7:12\">REV 7:11–7:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev11:16\">REV 11:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:8-Rev22:9\">REV 22:8–22:9</a></p>\n<h3>The redeemed</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:9\">1PE 2:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:11\">ISA 51:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:5-Rev19:7\">REV 19:5–19:7</a></p>\n<h3>The angels</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:13-Luke2:14\">LUK 2:13–2:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev5:11-Rev5:12\">REV 5:11–5:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:11\">REV 7:11</a></p>\n<h3>God is worshipped in song</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev15:2-Rev15:3\">REV 15:2–15:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:3\">REV 14:3</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ is worshipped in heaven</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:10-Phil2:11\">PHP 2:10–2:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:14\">DAN 7:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:6\">HEB 1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev5:8-Rev5:14\">REV 5:8–5:14</a></p>\n<h2>All heaven serves God</h2>\n<h3>God's will is perfectly done in heaven</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:10\">MAT 6:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:50\">MAT 12:50</a></p>\n<h3>The redeemed will serve God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:3\">REV 22:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev5:10\">REV 5:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:13-Rev7:15\">REV 7:13–7:15</a></p>\n<h3>The redeemed will reign with Jesus Christ and share his authority</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:28\">MAT 19:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:34\">MAT 25:34</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:3\">1CO 6:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:12\">2TI 2:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:28\">HEB 12:28</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:26-Rev2:27\">REV 2:26–2:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:21\">REV 3:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:6\">REV 20:6</a></p>\n<h2>The divine service of angels</h2>\n<h3>They have divine authority</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev8:2\">REV 8:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:1\">REV 18:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:1\">REV 20:1</a></p>\n<h3>They serve Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:31\">MAT 25:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:53\">MAT 26:53</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:10\">LUK 4:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:43\">LUK 22:43</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:7-2Thess1:8\">2TH 1:7–1:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:6\">HEB 1:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:22\">1PE 3:22</a></p>\n<h3>They serve believers</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:5-1Kgs19:8\">1KI 19:5–19:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:31\">MAT 24:31</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:14\">HEB 1:14</a></p>\n<h3>They serve by encouraging</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen21:17\">GEN 21:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:43\">LUK 22:43</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts27:23-Acts27:24\">ACT 27:23–27:24</a></p>\n<h3>They serve by guarding</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:19\">EXO 14:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:15-2Kgs6:17\">2KI 6:15–6:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps91:11\">PSA 91:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:10\">MAT 18:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:2-Rev7:3\">REV 7:2–7:3</a></p>\n<h3>They serve by instructing</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen22:11\">GEN 22:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen22:15\">GEN 22:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech6:5\">ZEC 6:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt1:20\">MAT 1:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:13\">MAT 2:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:5-Matt28:7\">MAT 28:5–28:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:13\">LUK 1:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:19\">LUK 1:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:26\">ACT 8:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:3-Acts10:5\">ACT 10:3–10:5</a></p>\n<h3>They serve by delivering believers in trouble</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:22\">DAN 6:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:19\">ACT 5:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:7\">ACT 12:7</a></p>\n<h3>Their service is continuous</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen28:12\">GEN 28:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:51\">JHN 1:51</a></p>",
